<% content_for :title do %>Three Wise Men Inc. Software Development and Consulting<% end %>
<% content_for :description do %>We provide outsourced application development and consulting services to either replace or complement in-house development talent. We also help companies improve their own software development practices by adopting agile processes and tools.<% end %>
<% content_for :keywords do %>java, ruby on rails, ruby, xml, xsl, xsl:fo, xslt, content management, content transformation, content publishing, multi-tenant content management<% end %>

<div class="mainpanel">
  <p>
    We help organizations make deadlines and keep budgets. In today’s world of reduced resources
    and increased expectations, Stakeholders and IT professionals alike call on us to cut through
    the seemingly endless minutia that can suffocate a project.
  </p>
  <p>
    Practitioners of agile and lean software application development, we don’t spend your budget
    on meaningless window dressing. We identify clear and concise targets for your project then
    develop it.
  </p>
  <p>
    <em>Backed by extensive testing projects are operational on time and within budget.</em>
  </p>
</div>
<div class="service1">
    <%= link_to image_tag("/images/development-trans.png"), :action => "development" %>
    <h2>Application Development</h2>
    <p>
        Unparalleled technical skill and the world's best open-source foundations at your disposal.
    </p>
    <p class="more"><%= link_to "read more...", { :action => "development" }, :class => "linkmarker" %></p>
</div>
<div class="service2">
    <%= link_to image_tag("/images/consulting-trans.png"), :action => "consulting" %>
    <h2>Consulting</h2>
    <p>
        A critical eye, creative and practical
        solutions for your tough problems.
    </p>
    <p class="more"><%= link_to "read more...", { :action => "consulting" }, :class => "linkmarker" %></p>
</div>
<div class="service3">
    <%= link_to image_tag("/images/apphosting-trans.png"), :action => "hosting" %>
    <h2>Application Hosting</h2>
    <p>
        Unparalleled 100% uptime guarantee for qualified applications.
    </p>
    <p class="more"><%= link_to "read more...", { :action => "hosting" }, :class => "linkmarker" %></p>
</div>
<div class="bottom"></div>

<div id="blog">
  <h1><span style="color: #aaa">Latest blog from our CEO:</span> <%= @blog_item.title %></h1>
  <p>
      <%= @blog_item.summary.gsub(/\s+\[\.\.\.\]/, "...") %>
      <%= link_to "read more...", { :action => "blogentry", :id => blog_strip_id(@blog_item.id) }, :class => "linkmarker" %>
  </p>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
  $("#blog").corner("11px");
</script>